---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Community - Antarctica DAO">
	<h1>Join the Antarctica DAO Community</h1>
	
	<section>
		<h2>Connect, Collaborate, and Contribute</h2>
		<p>Antarctica DAO thrives on the passion and expertise of its community members. Join us in shaping the future of decentralized social media and the Farcaster ecosystem.</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Community Channels</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>Discord:</strong> Our primary hub for discussions, collaborations, and support.
				<a href="#" class="channel-link">Join our Discord</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Twitter:</strong> Follow us for the latest news, announcements, and insights.
				<a href="#" class="channel-link">Follow @AntarcticaDAO</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>GitHub:</strong> Contribute to our open-source projects and initiatives.
				<a href="#" class="channel-link">Explore our repositories</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Forum:</strong> Engage in in-depth discussions and governance proposals.
				<a href="#" class="channel-link">Visit our forum</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Get Involved</h2>
		<p>There are many ways to contribute to the Antarctica DAO community:</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Develop:</strong> Build applications, tools, or infrastructure for the Farcaster ecosystem</li>
			<li><strong>Research:</strong> Contribute to technical research and protocol improvements</li>
			<li><strong>Educate:</strong> Create tutorials, articles, or videos to help others learn about Farcaster</li>
			<li><strong>Moderate:</strong> Help maintain a positive and productive community environment</li>
			<li><strong>Translate:</strong> Assist in making our resources available in multiple languages</li>
			<li><strong>Design:</strong> Contribute your creative skills to improve user experiences and visual communications</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Community Events</h2>
		<p>Stay tuned for regular community events, including:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Monthly community calls</li>
			<li>Hackathons and coding challenges</li>
			<li>AMAs with Farcaster developers and ecosystem partners</li>
			<li>Workshops and training sessions</li>
			<li>Virtual meetups and networking events</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Code of Conduct</h2>
		<p>We are committed to providing a welcoming and inclusive community for everyone. Please review our <a href="#">Code of Conduct</a> to understand our community guidelines and expectations.</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Start Your Journey</h2>
		<p>Ready to dive in? Join our Discord server to introduce yourself and start connecting with fellow community members!</p>
		<a href="#" class="cta-button">Join Antarctica DAO Discord</a>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	ul {
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.channel-link {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background-color: var(--accent-color);
		color: var(--background-color);
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 5px;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}
	.cta-button:hover {
		background-color: var(--text-color);
	}
</style>